desc
@Monte Carlo convergence graph
@


15.5
log
@Further work to adapt to new Gnuplot syntax.
@
text
@# Copyright 2002 D. C. Hatton
#
# D. C. Hatton can be contacted on dan.hatton@@btinternet.com
